Package KioskApp.Inventory

package KioskApp.Inventory
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    BakeryItem
    A class that represents an item from the bakery department, inheriting from Item.
    CreateAndStoreItems
    A class with methods that allows for the creation of various objects inherited from Item and for the items to be stored in ItemList.csv There are methods that allow users to create bakery, dairy, frozen, pantry, and misc item objects and there is a method that stores the items in ItemList.csv.
    CreateAndStoreItemsDriver
    This is a class that allows a user to easily add items to ItemList.csv, which in turn allows the items to be available in the program.
    DairyItem
    A class that represents an item from the dairy department, inheriting from Item.
    FrozenItem
    A class that represents an item from the Frozen department, inheriting from Item.
    ImportItems
    This is a class that imports items to KioskApp by retrieving them from the ItemList.csv file.
    Item
    Class of items to be used for items in grocery stores.
    MiscItem
    A class that represents an item from the Miscellaneous department, inheriting from Item.
    PantryItem
    A class that represents an item from the Pantry department, inheriting from Item.
    ProduceItem
    A class that represents an item from the Produce department, inheriting from Item.
